data.description: Welcome to your charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo with a private patio, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step into a space where modern updates meet cozy living - with 844 square feet of living space, this condo is designed to optimize every inch for your convenience.  The interior boasts recently updated flooring and a renovated bathroom, providing a fresh and contemporary feel throughout. An updated kitchen with white cabinets, stainless steel appliances and an open layout that flows into the living room, making it ideal for entertaining with friends and family.   One of the highlights of this condo is its thoughtful design, including a full-size washer and dryer for your laundry needs. The new sliding glass door not only adds a lot of natural light, but it walks out to the private patio, making it super convenient for morning coffee, evening relaxation or easy access to the open space behind the condo - perfect for pets!    Enjoy the convenience of a pet-friendly environment, allowing your furry friends to roam and play. With the open layout, contemporary updates, and access to outdoor space, this condo truly has it all.  Ideally located near downtown Leesburg with access to endless shopping, dining and commuter roads.  And don't forget about the parking!  Not only an assigned space, right out the front door, but an entire row of ample, additional parking!!   Don't miss the opportunity to make this condo your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and elegance that awaits you in this delightful home.
